<p>The lights suddenly go out and there is a commotion among the guests. After a short while, one of Charles' staff was able to get the lights back on. Seconds after the lights turn back on, someone suddenly yells. You turn towards the sound and you see Charles' lifeless body on the ground. You immediately look around him to take note of who are near him. These people will become your prime suspects. As you look around, you realize that the only people near him are his children.</p>
